<item>
  <title>Null space and Column space</title>
  <link>https://cryscham123.github.io/posts/02_areas/선형대수/notes/10.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p><img src="https://cryscham123.github.io/img/human-thumb.jpg" class="post-thumbnail img-fluid"></p>
<section id="metrix-vector-product" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="metrix-vector-product">Metrix vector product</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li>See <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A">’s column space as a set of vectors. → <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A">’s column space is the set of all linear combinations of the columns of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A">.</li>
<li>See <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?B">’s row space as a set of vectors.</li>
</ol>
</section>
<section id="null-space" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="null-space">Null space</h2>
<dl>
<dt><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?N%20=%20%5C%7Bx%20%5Cin%20%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5En%20%7C%20Ax%20=%200%5C%7D"></dt>
<dd>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?N"> is Null space of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A">.</p>
</dd>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><p>N(A) = N(rref(A))</p></li>
<li><p>if N(A) = {0}, then column vector of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A"> is linearly independent. → column vector of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?A"> is not a basis for C(A) → pivot variable의 합이 free variable을 만든다. (redundant column)</p></li>
<li><p>dim(N(A)) = nullity of A = # of free variables in rref(A)</p></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="column-space" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="column-space">Column Space</h2>
<ul>
<li>C(A) = span(columns of A)</li>
<li>rref(A)의 pivot variable의 column vector가 C(A)의 basis이다.</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="column-space의-평면의-방정식" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="column-space의-평면의-방정식">Column Space의 평면의 방정식</h2>
<ul>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7B%5CrightVectorBar%7Bb%7D%20%7C%20A%5CrightVectorBar%7Bx%7D%20=%20%5CrightVectorBar%7Bb%7D%20%E2%88%A7%20%5CrightVectorBar%7Bx%7D%20%E2%88%88%20R%5En%7D"></p></li>
<li><p>위를 만족하는 기약행렬을 만들어, 해가 존재하도록 방정식을 구성하면 평면의 방정식을 구할 수 있다.</p></li>
<li><p>혹은 column space의 basis를 구하고, 이를 이용해 평면의 방정식을 구할 수 있다.</p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?R%5En">을 span하는 basis의 vector는 n개이다.</p></li>
</ul>


</section>

