<p><img src="https://cryscham123.github.io/img/human-thumb.jpg" class="post-thumbnail img-fluid"></p>
<section id="dot-product" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="dot-product">Dot Product</h2>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%E2%8B%85%20w%20=%20%5Csum_%7Bi=1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20v_i%20w_i"></li>
</ul>
<section id="properties" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="properties">Properties</h3>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%E2%8B%85%20w%20=%20w%20%E2%8B%85%20v"></li>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%E2%8B%85%20(w%20+%20u)%20=%20v%20%E2%8B%85%20w%20+%20v%20%E2%8B%85%20u"></li>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%E2%8B%85%20(c%20w)%20=%20c%20(v%20%E2%8B%85%20w)"></li>
</ul>
</section>
</section>
<section id="length-of-vector" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="length-of-vector">Length of vector</h2>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20=%20%5Csqrt%7Bv%20%E2%8B%85%20v%7D"></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="some-properties" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="some-properties">Some properties</h2>
<p>for non-zero vectors <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v"> and <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?w">:</p>
<section id="cauchy-schwarz-inequality" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="cauchy-schwarz-inequality">cauchy-schwarz inequality</h3>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7Cv%20%E2%8B%85%20w%7C%20%E2%89%A4%20%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20%7C%7Cw%7C%7C"></li>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7Cv%20%E2%8B%85%20w%7C%20=%20%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20%7C%7Cw%7C%7C"> ⟺ <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20=%20cw"></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="triangle-inequality" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="triangle-inequality">Triangle inequality</h3>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7C%7Cv%20+%20w%7C%7C%20%E2%89%A4%20%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20+%20%7C%7Cw%7C%7C"></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="angle-between-vectors" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="angle-between-vectors">Angle between vectors</h3>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?cos%CE%B8%20=%20%5Cfrac%7Bv%20%E2%8B%85%20w%7D%7B%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20%7C%7Cw%7C%7C%7D"></li>
<li>if <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v"> and <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?w"> are orthogonal, then <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%E2%8B%85%20w%20=%200"></li>
</ul>
</section>
</section>
<section id="cross-product" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="cross-product">Cross Product</h2>
<ul>
<li><p>only for 3D vectors</p></li>
<li><p>get a vector that is orthogonal to both <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v"> and <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?w"></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%C3%97%20w%20=%20(v_2%20w_3%20-%20v_3%20w_2,%20v_3%20w_1%20-%20v_1%20w_3,%20v_1%20w_2%20-%20v_2%20w_1)"></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?sin%CE%B8%20=%20%5Cfrac%7B%7C%7Cv%20%C3%97%20w%7C%7C%7D%7B%7C%7Cv%7C%7C%20%7C%7Cw%7C%7C%7D"></p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v%20%C3%97%20w%20=%200"> ⟺ <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?v"> and <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?w"> are parallel</p></li>
<li><p>v와 w로 이루어진 평행사변형의 넓이는 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%7C%7Cv%20%C3%97%20w%7C%7C">이다.</p></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="triple-productlagrange-identity" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="triple-productlagrange-identity">Triple product(lagrange identity)</h2>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?a%20x%20(b%20x%20c)%20=%20b(a%20%E2%8B%85%20c)%20-%20c(a%20%E2%8B%85%20b)"></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="차원의-평면에서-직선의-방정식" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="차원의-평면에서-직선의-방정식">3차원의 평면에서 직선의 방정식</h2>
<ul>
<li><p>평면에 대한 법선벡터 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?(a,%20b,%20c)">와 평면 위의 한 점 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?(x_p,%20y_p,%20z_p)">이 주어졌을 때, 평면의 방정식은 다음과 같다.</p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?ax%20+%20by%20+%20cz%20=%20D">, <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?D%20=%20ax_p%20+%20by_p%20+%20cz_p"></p></li>
<li><p>평행한 평면은 a, b, c의 계수가 같은 평면이다.</p></li>
<li><p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%5Cfrac%7BAx_0%20+%20By_0%20+%20Cz_0%20+%20D%7D%7B%5Csqrt%7BA%5E2%20+%20B%5E2%20+%20C%5E2%7D%7D">은 평면과 점 <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?(x_0,%20y_0,%20z_0)"> 사이의 거리이다.</p></li>
