<item>
  <title>Subspaces and the basis</title>
  <link>https://cryscham123.github.io/posts/02_areas/선형대수/notes/07.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p><img src="https://cryscham123.github.io/img/human-thumb.jpg" class="post-thumbnail img-fluid"></p>
<section id="subspaces" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="subspaces">Subspaces</h2>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?S"> is a subset of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?V">.
<ol type="1">
<li>S ⊆ V</li>
<li>S is a vector space
<ol type="1">
<li>include zero vector</li>
<li>closed under addition</li>
<li>closed under scalar multiplication</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="basis" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="basis">Basis</h2>
<ul>
<li>minimum set of vectors that spans the subset</li>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?S"> is a basis of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?V"> ⟺
<ol type="1">
<li>elements of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?S"> are linearly independent</li>
<li><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?S"> spans <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?V"></li>
</ol></li>
<li>특정 부분집합의 basis의 linear combination으로 표현되는 모든 벡터는 유일하다.</li>
</ul>


</section>

